Package: a14-charge-keeper
Version: 0.3.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), upower, systemd
Maintainer: lollolha97 <lollolha97@gmail.com>
Description: Battery charge threshold manager for Linux laptops
 A lightweight command-line tool for managing battery charging limits
 on supported laptops including ASUS TUF A14, ThinkPad, and other models
 that support Linux kernel sysfs battery control interfaces.
 .
 Features:
  * Set battery charge end threshold (20-100%)
  * Support for ThinkPad charge start threshold
  * Automatic reapplication after boot/resume
  * Hardware compatibility checking
  * Backup and rollback functionality
Homepage: https://github.com/lollolha97/tuf-charge-keeper
